@node intro "Introduction"

                                Introduction
                                ------------

DFB FileList Generator is obviously a file list generator for DFB 1.2, the
Max's BBS Replacement Filebase :). This lister is one of the first of it's
type for DFB and is one of the best FileListers available for any Max's
Filebase. DFB FileList Generator has the following features.

- Full gadtools GUI - WB2/3 style.
- Linear ASCII List
- Sorted ASCII List
- 2 types of AmigaGuide List. *
- Section Names Configurable & Optional
- Allows choice of which details to output
- Allows a text header to be added at the start. ** 
- Use Reqtools File Requestors
- Allows purging of FileBase 
- Easy to use!


* Limited to 100 Files in the unregistered version.
** Only available in the registered version.

DFB FileList Generator 2.02 will now been referred to as DFB-FLG 2.02!

@endnode

