@node shareware "Shareware"

                              Shareware Info
                              --------------

DFB-FLG is Shareware, if you register using the Registration form included
in the archive you will receive the full version which has the following
extra features.

- List Headers  * Gives you the choice of adding a textfile of any
                  size at the start of the output list, so you could place
                  a BBS advert or just general information that you want
                  your users to know.

- AmigaGuide List  * Generates a choice of 2 types of AmigaGuide files for
                     ALL your files in your filebase instead of being 
                     limited to 100

and:-

- No '*** UNREGISTERED SHAREWARE VERSION ***' notices, both in the DFB-FLG
  itself and the file lists it produces.

- NO Jelly Zone BBS advert in the final file list.

- The Shareware Requestor is removed from the start!

- Up to 2 FREE Registered Updates (by request and if available) sent either
  by E-mail or picked up by yourself via modem. Or by sending enough money
  to cover postage and packing.

NB
--
The 1st registered version will be sent to you from your choice of the
following, Via E-Mail, On disk by Snail-Mail ( + P&P), or uploaded to a BBS
of your choice (UK only), or of course if you're willing you can pick it up
directly by modem.


