@node history "Program History"

V1.0 - ASCII and Amigaguide file list makers were actually separate
       programs and only really considered as early beta versions 
 
V2.0 - Totally re-written - see features

V2.02 - Changed the Reqtools flag so you can only select an output path as
        the filename wasn't used.
      - Fixed some serious bugs in that it didn't always read files
        correctly especially if you used a lot of Alias's
@endnode

