@node MN "Maxs Net II"

                                Maxs Net II
                                -----------

Maxs Net II is a network designed as an alternative to the original Maxs
Network, however it covers a much broader spectrum. We even have several
Zeus, Xenolink, Daydream and TransAmiga BBS's connected. The main theme is
BBS'ing in general and the development of/for BBS's.

MN2 is for both the experienced and the inexperienced alike!

The network has many other areas such as general chat, coding and the like,
it isn't purely BBS's although thats it's theme.

On MN2 we have many experienced programmers in ASM, C, E, Blitz & Amos and
developers for Maxs such as the author of Maxs Pro (real time patch),
SpinDiz, RIP Patch, Amiquote and the authors of new and upcomming BBS 
Software, Mirage and Spud. Many of the doors released for Maxs are being
converted for use with other systems such as Zeus.

For more information:

The Jelly Zone 01325 321172 9pm - 8am

@endnode
